				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\upmu$$\end{document}bar for 600 secs in Ar gas atmosphere with an applied power of 100 W at room temperature. To have an estimation of the final Au film thickness, Au was also simultaneously deposited on a bare Si substrate for 600 s16. X-ray reflectivity fitting of this film had yielded Au film thickness of dAu\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
